trans-unit.source: Disable RTE: If this option is set the config for RTE will not load automatically. Include "FILE:EXT:bulma_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/RTE.tsconfig" in your PageTsConfig to load the config manually.
trans-unit.target: RTE deaktivieren: Wenn diese Option gesetzt ist, wird die Konfiguration für RTE nicht automatisch geladen. Fügen Sie "FILE:EXT:bulma_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/RTE.tsconfig" in Ihre PageTsConfig ein, um die Konfiguration manuell zu laden.

trans-unit.source: Disable Processing of Scss files: WARNING: If this option is set there no more automatic processing of Scss files in the frontend. You will need to provide CSS files instead or handle the processing of the Scss files yourself.
